{"tid":734342,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 逆向思維：騎劫粵港澳大灣區，推動廣東獨立！","createTime":"2018-07-08T14:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T06:44:15.000Z","uid":35699,"like":235,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"cf67d18198ca1af40ba04dd5f5a73339e45a8a67","tid":734342,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T14:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/221518_1392e14132d90610a35c9745379da7ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F221518_1392e14132d90610a35c9745379da7ae.jpg&h=69871fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>近日侵侵集中火力攻擊「中國製造2025」，另一邊廂有巴基斯坦佬玩殘「一帶一路」。咁小弟就忽發奇想，點解我地要當「大灣區」係中國既最新威脅，而唔可以反轉頭利用呢個「名詞」同中國共產黨忌諱既「本土」、甚至「獨立」扣上關係，繼而令中共本身既宣傳用語變成佢地既禁語。</em><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">跳出思想限制，「香港獨立」可以唔係「香港離開中國」！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家理解既「香港獨立」，通常都係「香港退出中國管治」，自決派既想像都係「香港人經過公投，選出獨立作為香港前途既方向」。但如果命運唔可以自決既時候呢？香港獨立就唔再係一個選項，而係必然發生既事。講白少少，就係當「中國」變得散收收既時候，香港就自然獨立，而變得散收收既第一步，竟然係運用「粵港澳大灣區」呢個中共最新推出既「共式名詞」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「粵港澳大灣區」涵蓋既地域啱啱好係廣東全境，廣東人都有類似既文化，而且大家都唔妥班北佬，目標一致既情況底下，廣東各部分組成鬆散既聯邦對大家都好，當廣東獨立成功後香港就可以享有實際既獨立，之後既野唔敢講，但起碼北佬唔會繼續好似宜家咁玩弄我地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我指出既唔係單純鼓勵廣東人幫香港人搞埋獨立，我相信大家喺過去二十年已經充分感受到民主唔會從天跌落黎，又或者從天跌落黎既民主總會一點一滴地消失；我意思係話，如果可以透過「粵港澳大灣區」呢個字，鼓勵到廣東人做少少野，擴大我地既力量，呢樣野你話幾好呢。退而求其次，將「粵港澳大灣區」同「分裂」、「獨立」緊緊扣連，都係瓦解中共宣傳攻勢既上佳武器。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e861235f290ecba8329dfecf0d6397e6c958b3","tid":734342,"uid":62226,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T14:25:57.000Z","msg":"咁鬼多撈佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2991230411459e44fa030656c85cc608523507d","tid":734342,"uid":81139,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T14:26:24.000Z","msg":"「粵港澳大灣區」涵蓋既地域啱啱好係廣東全境<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nup乜9"},{"pid":"806f56e71da9ff0a7ace403c2a0fe67ac193364f","tid":734342,"uid":123456,"like":57,"dislike":9,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T14:26:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">獨派成功擴大ff範圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"df65fe4276579208c59f825c75f501203b6564b0","tid":734342,"uid":89063,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T14:31:18.000Z","msg":"咁多北方人落廣州做嘢，點搞<br />\n我咁講仲要假設大灣區入面嘅原居大陸人想獨立"},{"pid":"e13cb0db8170b951c7a6d53a979b611faf420327","tid":734342,"uid":35699,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T14:35:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多北方人落廣州做嘢，點搞<br />\n我咁講仲要假設大灣區入面嘅原居大陸人想獨立</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係想佢地獨立，而係指出「大灣區獨立」呢樣野可以瘋狂吹奏，令中共可以放棄「大灣區」呢樣野。<br />\n<br />\n當中共再推第二樣「口號」出黎既時候，我地都要好似侵侵同蝻一樣咁玩爛佢個新口號，瓦解整個輿論宣傳系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9b983616afbf21b89c29d694bf23f01ba54716","tid":734342,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T15:35:32.000Z","msg":"真係有圖！"},{"pid":"675592dd69aac26b73fed464d70e000db87ee64c","tid":734342,"uid":40216,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T15:37:55.000Z","msg":"大灣區＝南粵邦聯"},{"pid":"9c4a91fc1ef558d6c8d3b671154c604302fd8374","tid":734342,"uid":35776,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T15:38:08.000Z","msg":"廣東全境fail<br />\n廣東人&gt;深圳fail"},{"pid":"e820b5a74801583153aac1ded442004d72e065e3","tid":734342,"uid":52230,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"只要中國唔再干涉香港 政府取消每日150我已經夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817362263aeb3ea52de0cfe764414cd15953e439","tid":734342,"uid":90601,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T15:39:50.000Z","msg":"香港人連短短一條菜街都騎劫唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db88f37c2395e5f420a82026b0fb7d19c16bf7e2","tid":734342,"uid":68540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T19:22:36.000Z","msg":"大灣獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df3f7d221a5fc61136191c83a133442ba040fb7","tid":734342,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T19:50:32.000Z","msg":"不如話割讓比美國仲實際"},{"pid":"5e10f7a41cbd1557e09c9a8e20d8e6577985ebd2","tid":734342,"uid":28759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T19:53:06.000Z","msg":"同建制派偷咗法治 普選呢尖西字眼鳩 up 一樣道理<br />\n拎返老共啲口號嚟鳩 up"},{"pid":"31252a4505dad9bae43d50fdeac5c2de7bc810f1","tid":734342,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T19:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同建制派偷咗法治 普選呢<span style=\"color: red;\">啲</span>字眼鳩 up 一樣道理<br />\n拎返老共啲口號嚟鳩 up</blockquote><br />\n打錯字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7481fc7ba910d0dd0b0819cfbdaf915812d888","tid":734342,"uid":16970,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T19:57:08.000Z","msg":"剩係香港人嗌大灣區獨立, 你估北京會唔會驚? 正如剩係尖沙咀碼頭幾條友嗌香港獨立, 你估林鄭驚唔驚?"},{"pid":"1c44bd217de67aae587eba196219e49422c86ca4","tid":734342,"uid":15494,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T21:10:10.000Z","msg":"港獨連香港人都未說服得掂, 說服班支人更加冇可能"},{"pid":"421eef849dea8ed385664c1157a3ff0581e2804b","tid":734342,"uid":14230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T21:15:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a30f4403839e12